  "2334450": {
    "name": "幽灵捕手",
    "steam_appid": 2334450,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/fcbfc6db0d032334e93f6ddc425c79a0.avif?t=1738756345\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽灵捕手是一款合作式恐怖游戏，可由至少1名和最多8名玩家一起玩。你需要不断深入鬼屋，解锁新的区域，了解案件背后的真相；举行神秘仪式，与灵体周旋，识别它的类别，并最终将其回收</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/8146741f804f245cea2c3bac6a7ca71d.poster.avif?t=1738756345\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/8146741f804f245cea2c3bac6a7ca71d.webm?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/8146741f804f245cea2c3bac6a7ca71d.mp4?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/4e4f6d2f552f90383da0e1615a570fc6.webp?t=1738756345\" width=230 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中玩家可以变身为可爱的小猫，不仅能躲避灵体的猎杀，还能通过特殊视觉发现隐藏的道具，甚至与其它玩家互动，享受摸鱼的乐趣</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/38ccf3bce88aac827f3b1d340e9d628e.poster.avif?t=1738756345\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/38ccf3bce88aac827f3b1d340e9d628e.webm?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/38ccf3bce88aac827f3b1d340e9d628e.mp4?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/fb5459040b722fd88be6d0c8e4b11293.webp?t=1738756345\" width=230 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地图中寻找线索以增加探索度，了解更多隐藏在阴影中的故事，解锁更广阔的活动区域，增加进阶玩法，直到探明整个地图将筑巢在此的灵体彻底收服，以获取成就和特殊奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/0e4abaaa159f3de8a551e5f1f7297a52.poster.avif?t=1738756345\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/0e4abaaa159f3de8a551e5f1f7297a52.webm?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/0e4abaaa159f3de8a551e5f1f7297a52.mp4?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/96ef88443613d2ac714a60cf1bb8879d.webp?t=1738756345\" width=230 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次进入都会面对不同的灵体，完全随机的诅咒道具和遗物，还有千奇百怪的地图事件亟待解决，保证每局游戏都是不一样的体验，挑战永无止境</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/f691b8c156cb6dabd44425b6355758fe.poster.avif?t=1738756345\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/f691b8c156cb6dabd44425b6355758fe.webm?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/f691b8c156cb6dabd44425b6355758fe.mp4?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/11ab955d6d28cc670c136184bd82d5ad.webp?t=1738756345\" width=230 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你厌倦了在千篇一律的公寓室内玩过家家，想要一场更刺激的冒险，那么包括农场、以及未来即将推出的游乐园等一系列风格迥异，特色鲜明的魔窟等待你的征服</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/c7f04b98be1c1ca117e8d6034a7abfa6.poster.avif?t=1738756345\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/c7f04b98be1c1ca117e8d6034a7abfa6.webm?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/c7f04b98be1c1ca117e8d6034a7abfa6.mp4?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/a126abe681647bd18e4d46a49373fe19.webp?t=1738756345\" width=230 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里你能看到魅惑的恶魔招摇过市，圣洁的修女守望相助，更有美丽的法老与你并肩作伴，但是为了更加吸引目光，也许使用混搭风来展示自我也是个不错的选项，随你喜欢</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/b4711473e552176d6a7c39f7a75dd929.poster.avif?t=1738756345\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/b4711473e552176d6a7c39f7a75dd929.webm?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/b4711473e552176d6a7c39f7a75dd929.mp4?t=1738756345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334450/extras/9e98838758063ec4fb2ab6d348ef08f4.webp?t=1738756345\" width=230 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用虚幻5精心制作，更好的画面表现力，致力于带给玩家更强的沉浸感，体验最有代入感的驱魔之旅 </p>",
